## Educational Use Notice

This project is designed for educational purposes, specifically to teach children
about cellular biology and sleep science. While the software is provided under
the MIT License, we encourage users to:

1. Maintain scientific accuracy when modifying educational content
2. Consider the age-appropriateness of any changes for 10-year-old learners
3. Cite original research sources when using or adapting the scientific content
4. Respect the educational mission of making science accessible to young minds

## Attribution for Educational Content

While not required by the MIT License, we appreciate attribution when using
this project's educational approach or scientific content adaptations in other
educational contexts.

